Title: S5 Ep. 208 Johnny Williams
Description:
Our guest this week is Johnny Williams and he played professional NFL football. Want to know which team? You have to listen to our show to find that information out. He transitioned from football to the business world and started a company called Player Epic.  We talked about ghosts, the fact that he can rap, can play an instrument, and of course - the FIVE words that describe him.  Be sure to tune in, download and leave us a comment about what you liked about the show.
